        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "in measuring cups."
        },
        {
          "type": "section",
          "text": "Cell phones"
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• In Uganda, customers paid to use the cell phones of entrepreneurs."
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• These customers wanted to check the"
        },
        {
          "type": "gap",
          "number": 33
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "used."
        },
        {
          "type": "section",
          "text": "Computer companies"
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• There was a need to develop"
        },
        {
          "type": "gap",
          "number": 34
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "to improve communication between system administrators and colleagues."
        },
        {
          "type": "section",
          "text": "Hospitals"
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• Nurses needed to access information about"
        },
        {
          "type": "gap",
          "number": 35
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "in different parts of the hospital."
        },
        {
          "type": "section",
          "text": "Airlines"
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• Respondents recorded information about their"
        },
        {
          "type": "gap",
          "number": 36
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "while travelling."
        },
        {
          "type": "section",
          "text": "Principles of ethnographic research in business"
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• The researcher does not start off with a hypothesis."
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• Participants may be selected by criteria such as age,"
        },
        {
          "type": "gap",
          "number": 37
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "or product used."
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• The participants must feel"
        },
        {
          "type": "gap",
          "number": 38
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "about taking part in the research."
        },
        {
          "type": "static",
          "text": "• There is usually direct"
